Gur cebtenz vzcyrzragf n fb pnyyrq Xevivar znpuvar,
raunaprq jvgu n onfvp vachg/bhgchg flfgrz
naq n ersrerapr pbhagvat tneontr pbyyrpgbe.
Gur Xevivar znpuvar vf n fgrcjvfr genafsbezre bs n tybony fgngr pbafvfgvat bs
gur pheerag grez, gur pheerag raivebazrag (n yvfg bs pybfherf), naq n fgnpx bs pbagvahngvbaf
(Frr gur 3eq ersrerapr sbe qrgnvyf.)

Gur grez fcnpr ubyqf ynzoqn pnyphyhf grezf va gur sbyybjvat sbezng
0 qrabgrf fbzr sbez bs VB; gur bayl sbhe bpphenaprf ner ng
  P=13: erpbtavmrf raq bs n olgr
  P=20: erpbtavmr bhgchg bs 0 ovg
  P=21: erpbtavmr bhgchg bs 1 ovg
  P=raq: vachg yvfg, rkcnaqrq ynmvyl
1 qrabgrf n inevnoyr, jvgu arkg ragel vgf qr Oehvwa vaqrk
